<header class="py-4 bg-dark text-white">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="mb-1">Badges &amp; Awards</h1>
    <p class="mb-0">Every badge has a rule. Cross the line, earn the badge. Receipts included.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="container my-4">
  <div class="row g-3">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div class="cardish p-3 h-100">
        <h2 class="h5">Finance Badges</h2>
        <ul class="mb-0">
          <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-dollar me-1 text-danger"></i>High PAC Reliance</strong>: PAC ≥ <code>40%</code> of itemized dollars.</li>
          <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-route me-1 text-warning"></i>Out‑of‑State Heavy</strong>: Out‑of‑state dollars &gt; in‑state dollars (by &gt;5%).</li>
          <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-industry me-1 text-danger"></i>Dominant Industry</strong>: One industry ≥ <code>35%</code> of itemized dollars.</li>
          <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced me-1 text-danger"></i>Donor‑Aligned Voting</strong>: Donor alignment index ≥ <code>90%</code>.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6" id="thresholds">
      <div class="cardish p-3 h-100">
        <h2 class="h5">Bill “Receipt” Badges</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">Assigned per bill page based on vote + justification mismatch.</p>
        <ul class="mb-0">
          <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice-dollar me-1 text-danger"></i>Sold the Vote</strong>: Vote + finance pattern matches beneficiary industry and contradicts stated rationale.</li>
          <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation me-1 text-danger"></i>Against Working Families</strong>: “No” on cost‑cutting bills with district benefits documented.</li>
          <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved me-1 text-warning"></i>Process Abuse</strong>: Rider/block tactics to kill a clean up‑or‑down vote.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cardish p-3 mt-3">
    <h2 class="h6">Where do these numbers come from?</h2>
    <p class="mb-0">Nightly pipeline pulls FEC data, aggregates by member and industry, and computes alignment indices. See <code>data/*.json</code> in the repo. Finance badges render on both the Wall and the Financial page.</p>
  </div>
</main>

